### 1. Add a Bill
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docNo": "BILL-001",
  "date": "2026-01-04"
}

###

### 2. Add a Product to that Bill
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/BILL-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ianNumber": "IAN-999",
  "price": 450.00
}

###

### 3. Search by IAN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/search/IAN-999